text: José Aguilar Martinez (born 5 February 2001) is a Spanish professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for the club Sion. ==Professional career== Aguilar made his professional debut with Sion in a 1-0 Swiss Super League loss to FC Thun 25 May 2019. ==References== ==External links== * * SFL Profile * Bild Profile Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:People from Almería Category:Spanish footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FC Sion players Category:Swiss Super League players Category:Spanish expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Switzerland Category:Spanish expatriates in Switzerland
